@ConferenceExample.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5185

### Create Conference
POST {{ConferenceExample.API_HostAddress}}/api/conferences
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "DotNet Conf 2026",
  "start": "2026-09-15T09:00:00+00:00",
  "end": "2026-09-17T18:00:00+00:00",
  "locationName": "Berlin Congress Center",
  "street": "Alexanderplatz 1",
  "city": "Berlin",
  "state": "Berlin",
  "postalCode": "10178",
  "country": "Germany"
}

###

### Submit Talk
POST {{ConferenceExample.API_HostAddress}}/api/talks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_SPEAKER_JWT_TOKEN>

{
  "title": "Clean Architecture in Practice",
  "abstract": "A deep dive into applying Clean Architecture principles in a real-world .NET application.",
  "conferenceId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "talkTypeId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
  "tags": ["dotnet", "architecture", "ddd"]
}

###
